      "updated_at": "2016-06-07 11:49:21 UTC",
      "body": "shocon is right now used in akka-js as a \"drop in\" replacement of typesafe config.\r\nIt is developed by @evacchi, it works, but it is not complete.\r\nIf you want to give a try use\r\n```\r\n\"eu.unicredit\" %%% \"shocon\" % \"0.0.2-SNAPSHOT\"\r\n```\r\nfrom \r\n```\r\nresolvers += \"sonatype-snapshots\" at \"https://oss.sonatype.org/content/repositories/snapshots\"\r\n```\r\nWe will be happy to support!"
    },
