      "created_at": "2016-06-07 19:17:43 UTC",
      "updated_at": "2016-06-07 19:17:43 UTC",
      "body": "> Why does scalafmt need to be Scala.js compatible?\r\n\r\nI want make a browser extension that formats Scala code on Github with scalafmt. If #315 gets implemented then then scalafmt-core will depend on the parser for the configuration language.\r\n\r\nDoes YAML support multiple statements on the same line? Like `a=1;b=2`."
    },
    {
